---
title: One-Pot Chicken & Couscous With Red Pesto & Basil
description: Love a one-pot wonder? Well, this one's for you! With succulent chicken breast, zingy lemon pepper spice blend and our flavour bomb red pesto, this is an easy-to-make, amazing-to-eat couscous sensation.
